{"id":"8788","user":{"id":"101860","nickname":"四片叶de三叶吖","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FqcR23gyTBxqpGDVypZpJe8hw4uq","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【少院士讲堂】第九课—BOX2.0课程倒计时；第二弹：桥的故事~","content":"<p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FnQEhiZRRDJV3-qmrwxFxDIO9H-6\"><br></p> \n<img>================================================================\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"4\">大家好 ~又是我，尚冲，上一期我们建造了中国建筑的垂花门，本期我们来讲一下：桥的故事</font></p>\n<p>================================================================</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;建筑主题：喵不看小标题</p>\n<p>================================================================&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"6\"><font color=\"#00ff00\">~</font><font color=\"#008080\">正文君</font><font color=\"#008000\">~</font></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"6\"><font color=\"#008000\"><br></font></font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"5\">&nbsp; q i á o</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</font><font size=\"7\">桥</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">一.桥的种类（<font color=\"#ffcc00\">一波芝士~</font>）</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">拱桥</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp;</font>中国拱桥建筑历史悠久。在古代桥梁中，以 拱桥 拱桥 石拱桥为主要桥型。无论在山谷、丘陵、平原和水网地区，至今仍存在各种风采的石拱桥。像十七孔桥，赵州桥........&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 优点： 1、跨越能力大； 2、能充分做到就地取材； 3、耐久性好，养护维修费用少； 4、外形美观； 5、构造简单，易于掌握。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 缺点： 1、自重较大，相应的水平推力大； 2、支架施工多、施工工序多、不便于机械化施工、施工周期长； 3、多孔拱桥需设单向推力墩</p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">细化：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</font> 按照拱轴线的型式可分为：圆弧拱桥、抛物线拱桥、悬链线拱桥</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;圆弧拱桥： 拱圈轴线按部分圆弧线设置的拱桥。优点构造简单，石料规格最少，备料、施工都很简便；缺点是受荷时拱内压力线偏离拱轴线较大，受力不均匀。一般适用于跨度较小的石拱桥。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;抛物线拱桥： 拱圈轴线按抛物线设置的拱桥。优点是弯矩小，材料省，跨越能力较大；缺点是构造较复杂，施工较不方便。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;悬链线拱桥： 拱圈轴线按悬链线设置的拱桥。优点是受力均匀，弯矩不大，节省材料。多适用于实腹拱桥，大跨度的空腹拱桥中也常常采用这种线形布置。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"https://ss1.bdstatic.com/70cFvXSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=2241067682,1275678317&amp;fm=200&amp;gp=0.jpg\">迷之拱桥<br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">梁桥</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; </font>梁桥一般建在跨度很大，水域较浅处，由桥柱和桥板组成，物体重量从桥板传向桥柱。以受弯为主的主梁作为承重构件的桥梁。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"4\">简支梁桥：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>简支梁是静定结构，相邻各跨单独受力，结构受力比较单纯，不受支座变位等影响，适用于各种地质情况，构造也较简单，方便，是一种采用最广 泛的梁式桥。</p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 连续梁桥：</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 结构由连续跨过三个以上支座的梁作为主 要承重结构的桥梁。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"4\">悬臂梁桥：</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 由锚固孔、悬臂和悬挂孔组成，悬挂孔支承在悬臂上，用铰相联。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ss2.bdstatic.com/70cFvnSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=304897862,3330539226&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg\"><img src=\"http://img3.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=1967251579,1127556416&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg\"><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">吊桥：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>吊桥又称悬索桥，由悬索、桥塔、吊杆、锚锭、加劲梁及桥面系所组成。吊桥的跨越能力是各种桥梁体系中最大的。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;传力途径简捷、明确。悬索桥的特点是：构造简单，受力明确；在同等条件下，跨径愈大，单位跨度的材料耗费愈少、造价愈低。悬索桥是大跨桥梁的主要形式。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/70cFvHSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=2778128361,3133630135&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg\"><br></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ss2.bdstatic.com/70cFvnSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=3633178161,2355162909&amp;fm=200&amp;gp=0.jpg\"><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">二.实践开始</font><br></p>\n<p>说这么多，建筑才是最重要的嘛，开始建造！</p>\n<p>小型石拱桥</p>\n<p>难度：</p>\n<p>技术程度：</p>\n<p>先立个桩，暂时把虚空当作河吧&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FvYXXSkYvJcn0N7lrCYJdJbPFcdq\"><br></p>\n<p>塑造基本型</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fh5wjVLP6SR71POVKLH1nYB3I81C\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>两边同时开工，要对称</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgjaB_cjiu4qM-IwB2dGIlAgGeTL\"><br></p>\n<p>细节修改，形成拱形</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FpFNh3S-YD4dj5MArv2CBE5q2ZTm\"><br></p>\n<p>铺上</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fiq-sZvfmcwdKVd91TMSZ6IrrGNa\"><br></p>\n<p>做好修饰，完工图</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FkYFzG1-zoauv1eZeg4b43XdED1w\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>中大型吊桥</p>\n<p>难度：</p>\n<p>技术程度：</p>\n<p>立两个柱子做吊索</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FiZl3q9NtuzTNBOVFC1nF3q2AtJT\"><br></p>\n<p>开铺桥面</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgXMgi5Nglj6s_CGXPy0hi2am-Ox\"><br></p>\n<p>双层的</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FkIXRyWMF6UHh-7wPvnRbQ9HuG6U\"><br></p>\n<p>加高两柱+细节</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhTdeogGjzXndfIN9iEMzBNYHjD4\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>放吊绳</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FnPO_5bOWUdtcvvPQLy0vuWQs5tH\"><br></p>\n<p>桥梁的建造就到这里啦~\\()/~大家最后一期见</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<iframe frameborder=\"no\" width=\"280\" height=\"86\" src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=30987703&amp;auto=1&amp;height=66\"></iframe></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font size=\"6\"> THANK YOU FOR YOUR READING~</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"6\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Have a good time&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &n